item.title: THM_RootMe_Walkthrough
item.description: RootMe TryHackMe performed by: jb-williams Deploy the machine Reconnaissance To get info on the target, run this nmap command: nmap -v -T4 -sV -sC -oA nmap/initial 10.10.105.101 This provides the answers to the following three questions. Scan the machine, how many ports ar open? Answer: 2 What version of Apache is running? Answer: 2.4.29 What service is running on port 22? Answer: ssh Find directories on the web server using the GoBuster tool.
